usage.excerpt:
1. Download [cityscapes dataset](https://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~tinghuiz/projects/pix2pix/datasets/cityscapes.tar.gz) and extract it. 
2. Run the script with `python3 pix2pix.py cityscapes`

That's it.
